# HerdFlow Project Rules

## Two Separate Applications

This project has TWO apps that must NEVER mix:

- herdflow-web/ = Next.js website (herdflow.co.za)
- herdflow-app/ = React Native Expo mobile app

## Prompt Prefixes Required

- Start with WEBSITE — for website changes
- Start with MOBILE APP — for mobile changes

## Brand Colors

Navy: #1B3A6B
Green: #2E7D32
Gold: #A07C3A
Tagline: Smarter Herds. Stronger Futures.

## Tech Stack

Website: Next.js TypeScript Tailwind Prisma PostgreSQL
Mobile: React Native Expo SQLite Zustand

## Rules

- Never hardcode colors use colors.ts or Tailwind
- TypeScript strict mode always no any types
- All data saves offline first then syncs to cloud
- Farm Workers cannot see financial data
- Every operation logs to activity_log
- Always use existing components before creating new ones
- Never mix website and mobile app code

## API Base URL

Production: https://www.herdflow.co.za/api
Development: http://localhost:3000/api

